  }, "Ethan Zuckerman:")), mdx("p", null, "Well, so I actually want to start by talking a little bit about your day job outside of the Public Spaces Coalition. What is VPRO, and even more broadly than that, how does public media in the Netherlands differ from public media we might understand like NPR in the US or the BBC in the UK?"), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
